  dialogueTurnsList:
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: f744c7f0aa979e14a931ddcfb4fb1faf, type: 2}
    dialogueLine: Therefore, I decided to take actions.
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: f744c7f0aa979e14a931ddcfb4fb1faf, type: 2}
    dialogueLine: I had to focus all my remaining power on one of the Earth's prettiest
      creatures. A lamb...
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: f744c7f0aa979e14a931ddcfb4fb1faf, type: 2}
    dialogueLine: Despite being too weak right now, I could recover all of my power
      easily.
  - character: {fileID: 11400000, guid: f744c7f0aa979e14a931ddcfb4fb1faf, type: 2}
    dialogueLine: But I'm not capable of doing so- I needed someone's help.
